5|$|In 646 Irbis Seguy of the Western Turks {{sought a}} Chinese princess for <b>his</b> <b>bride.</b> In return, Taizong asked for several Tarim Basin cities. Ibris' refusal {{was one of}} the pretexts for the war.|$|E
